The '''Azure Dianoga Cantina''' was a bar located in the [[Alien Protection Zone/Legends|Alien Protection Zone]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Imperial Center]]. It was used by members of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] as a meeting place while on an undercover mission before their [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|liberation]] of the world. The Rogues got into a conflict with the [[Alien Combine]] there.<ref name="WG">''[[X-Wing: Wedge's Gamble]]''</ref>

